headline: Savvas Learning Company Extends Collaboration with Cognizant, Leader in Driving Enterprise Transformation
summary: Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) announced today the continuation of its relationship with Savvas Learning Company with the aim to ensure that IT functions run seamlessly for the leading K-12 learning solutions provider, supporting its mission of delivering innovative, high-quality instructional materials to the millions of educators and students it serves.
